record_data.record_title: Co-Ten. SFA - C of C w/Clearwater Wind II
record_data.record_plain_text:
?CLEARWATER WIND III, LLC CERTIFICATE OF CONCURRENCE FOR CO-TENANCY SHARED FACILITIES AGREEMENT
This document certifies that Clearwater Wind III, LLC assents to and concurs with the Co-Tenancy Shared Facilities Agreement by and between Clearwater Wind II, LLC and Clearwater Wind III, LLC, described below, and files this Certificate of Concurrence in lieu of filing the specified agreement.
Joint Tariff Name/Description: Rate Schedule No. 1, Clearwater Wind II & Clearwater Wind III - Co-Tenancy SFA
Designated Filing Company: Clearwater Wind II, LLC
Designated Filing Company Tariff ID: Agreements (2)
Tariff Program: Federal Power Act Electric (Traditional Cost of Service & Market Based Rate) Public Utilities
Limitation to Incorporation by Reference: None (shall concur with all subsequent variations of agreement)
Clearwater Wind III, LLC By its duly authorized official /s/ Anthony Pedroni Vice President Dated November 19, 2024
record_data.filing_title: Co-Tenancy SFA Cert. of Concurrence with Clearwater Wind II
